The recommended Ruby gem is:

  https://github.com/gugod/libravatar


Testing
--------

Clone the module under ~/devel/remote/gravatar_url:

  cd ~/devel/remote/
  git clone git://github.com/gugod/libravatar.git libravatar-gem

Then put the test CGI under /var/www and create these symlinks:

  ln -s ~/devel/remote/libravatar-gem/lib/libravatar.rb /var/www/
